SUB_W02_EVAR_COMM_WHITE_AREA02_010_CUT_0.text:
We're pushing the crystals back bit by bit;
let this serve as proof that we witches
can continue our existence.

SUB_W02_EVAR_COMM_00_WORLDQUEST_MYSTERIO.text:
The witches of the black are fell;
they rule the world's waters, and take
joy in parching the forests and the land.

The witches of the white are skilled at deception;
their power of metal a nuisance which can
sever even the friendships of witches.
